Spec for my_first_blog

PHASE 1

author
	Basic blog with REST crud functions. 
		Author can sign in 
			Write a new article
			Update or delete existing articles

reader 
	view a list or articles (partially) on the home page
		5 at a time and trimmed to a teaser size
	click the headline or the (more) link to view the article in full

PHASE 2

	articles can be tagged
		articles can be organised by tags
	authors can upload images 
	Readers can comment
	Getting in touch page that emails a support email address